Entry.JapaneseText: どうやら里の者たちは、 敵地で命果てたようです……
Entry.EnglishText: It seems like most of the ninja in the village died in enemy territory...

Entry.JapaneseText: じゃあ、 プルートと戦う人が、 もうこの里にはいないの？
Entry.EnglishText: So there's no one to fight against Pluto in this village?
I knew it...Even with us this is...

Entry.JapaneseText: 里の精鋭の力をもってしても 突破できなかったのです
Entry.EnglishText: Without the village's elite soldiers our attack is heavily compromised...

Entry.JapaneseText: その敵地にこの少数で 潜入するなんて無茶です
Entry.EnglishText: With this small amount of people it is impossible to break through Pluto's territory...

Entry.JapaneseText: どうしてこんな時に、 私は里を留守に してしまったのでしょう……
Entry.EnglishText: Why did I have to leave the village in such a critical time...?

Entry.JapaneseText: 助けを呼んでくればいい？
Entry.EnglishText: Hey, is it ok if I ask for some help?

Entry.JapaneseText: <SUZ>ちゃんが ピンチだって言えば、 必ず飛んできてくれる人たち
Entry.EnglishText: People who I'm sure will come running here as soon as they hear you're in a pinch!

Entry.JapaneseText: ……呼ぶったって、 あの指輪で過去に行って……
Entry.EnglishText: ...She'll ask for help...And she was going to the past...?

Entry.JapaneseText: <SUZ>ちゃん！ ピンチなんだって！？
Entry.EnglishText: What do you mean my cute little <SUZ> is in trouble!?

Entry.JapaneseText: おまえ！ 声が大きい！
呼んできたよ、助っ人さんたちを
Entry.EnglishText: Told you I'd bring them, and here's the help!
It's nice to see you again, <SUZ>.
It has been a long time!

Entry.JapaneseText: なんだ、君たちも こんなところにいたのか
Entry.EnglishText: Oh look, you kids are here too.

Entry.JapaneseText: その節は お世話になりました
Entry.EnglishText: We are indebted to the help you gave us back then.

Entry.JapaneseText: わざわざこんなところまで 来ていただいてしまって…… 皆さん、大丈夫なのですか？
Entry.EnglishText: Coming from so far just specifically for this... Is this fine for all of you?

Entry.JapaneseText: ああ。とりあえず、 こっちはひと段落ついたし。 <DIO>たちのおかげでね
Entry.EnglishText: There's no problem here. We could finally take a break in our era...thanks to <DIO> and <MEL>, no less!

Entry.JapaneseText: 私の方の研究も まだ準備段階だしな
Entry.EnglishText: Ah, I've got time too. My research is only in its preparation stage.

Entry.JapaneseText: 本当にありがとうございます。 <RND_P>さんも大切な力を 私のために……
Entry.EnglishText: I am genuinely grateful to all of you... Thank you Rody to use your precious power for my cause...

Entry.JapaneseText: これは私たちの世界のため。 <MEL>ちゃんも言ってたっしょ
Entry.EnglishText: This is our world and therefore my responsibility. <MEL> said as much too, remember?

Entry.JapaneseText: ……でも、 ありがとうございます
Entry.EnglishText: ...And yet, thank you from the bottom of my heart.

Entry.JapaneseText: んじゃあ、みんな そろったし、行こうぜ！
Entry.EnglishText: Now that the all-star team is together, let's go!

Entry.JapaneseText: <Red>ネルヴィの洞窟<White>。 そこにプルートが
Entry.EnglishText: Pluto lies in the Norfi's Cave.
